      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>This collection consists of one Hollinger box containing
         one folder of miscellaneous materials and seven business
         ledgers that document operations of the Bowman family dairy
         farm in Rockingham County, VA, 1845- 1967, with the bulk of
         material covering 1941-1967.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <dsc type="combined">
