               <unittitle>Miscellaneous Materials: 
               <unitdate type="inclusive">
               1859-1960</unitdate></unittitle>
               <container label="Box-folder" type="Box-folder">
               1</container>
               <physdesc>Includes 1859 and 1865 tax receipts; 1862
               receipt for military supplies of 20 bushels of corn;
               1882 Constitution of the West Rockingham Mutual Fire
               Insurance Company; 1891 receipt for printing claim for
               property taken by U.S. soldiers in Civil War; 1929
               timber contract; 1942 Certificates of War Necessity for
               vehicle; summary of the S.R. Bowman Estate,
               1936-1960.</physdesc>
